The Lua language server provides various language features for Lua to
make development easier and faster.

Features:
- Supports Lua 5.4, Lua 5.3, Lua 5.2, Lua 5.1, and LuaJIT
- Over 20 supported annotations for documenting your code
- Go to definition
- Dynamic type checking
- Find references
- Diagnostics/Warnings
- Syntax checking
- Element renaming
- Hover to view details on variables, functions, and more
- Autocompletion
- Support for libraries
- Code formatting
- Spell checking
- Custom plugins
- Documentation Generation
